<td width="90%" valign="top" style="vertical-align: top">  
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<i>1.6.1 Vedligeholdelse af maskinen </i>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<i>Indstilling, pasning, reparation, rensning og vedligeholdelse af maskinen skal kunne foretages på maskinen, når denne er standset. </i>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<i>Maskindele, der ofte skal udskiftes på automatiserede maskiner, bl.a. på grund af en ændring i produktionen, eller fordi de ikke er slidstærke eller vil kunne beskadiges som følge af et uheld, skal let og sikkert kunne af- og påmonteres. </i>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<i>1.6.2 Adgangsveje til arbejdsstedet og interventionspunkter </i>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<br />
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/line.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->
<i>Fabrikanten skal forsyne maskinen med adgangsveje, trapper stiger, gangbroer osv., der gør det muligt sikkert at nå alle nødvendige steder i forbindelse med produktion, indstilling og vedligeholdelse.</i>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/emphasize.tpl) -->

  </td>

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/td.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/td.tpl) -->

